    <title type="html"><![CDATA[แปลงเลขฐานต่างๆ]]></title>
    <link href="http://cholwich.github.io/blog/2013/06/25/base-conversion/"/>
    <updated>2013-06-25T11:42:00+07:00</updated>
    <id>http://cholwich.github.io/blog/2013/06/25/base-conversion</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><code>int</code> ใช้สำหรับแปลง string แสดงเลขฐานต่างๆ ไปเป็นเลขค่าจำนวนเต็ม แล้วพิมพ์ออกมาเป็นฐานสิบได้ เช่น</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='python'><span class='line'><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="nb">int</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#39;3FF&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">16</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="mi">1023</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="nb">int</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#39;1010&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="mi">10</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p><code>hex</code> ใช้แปลงค่าจำนวนเต็ม ไปเป็น string เลขฐานสิบหก เช่น</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='python'><span class='line'><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="nb">hex</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1023</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s">&#39;0x3ff&#39;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="nb">hex</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">int</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#39;1010&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">))</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s">&#39;0xa&#39;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p><code>bin</code> ใช้แปลงค่าจำนวนเต็มไปเป็น string เลขฐานสอง เช่น</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='python'><span class='line'><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="nb">bin</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1023</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s">&#39;0b1111111111&#39;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="nb">bin</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">int</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#39;0xa&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">16</span><span class="p">))</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s">&#39;0b1010&#39;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="nb">bin</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mh">0xa</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s">&#39;0b1010&#39;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>

